360
00:28:13,333 --> 00:28:14,999
Phoenix?

361
00:28:15,208 --> 00:28:18,749
Yuen Po-wan wrote an excellent script.
I'm directing it.

362
00:28:18,916 --> 00:28:22,290
I want Phoenix for the lead.

363
00:28:24,416 --> 00:28:27,374
