389
00:29:58,916 --> 00:30:01,749
You're Flying Dagger Lee.

390
00:30:01,916 --> 00:30:03,582
Brilliant.

391
00:30:03,916 --> 00:30:05,749
Action.

392
00:30:16,500 --> 00:30:17,332
Where are the cops?

393
