551
00:42:28,291 --> 00:42:31,249
Stop it. Hurry up, we'll be late for school.

552
00:42:31,416 --> 00:42:33,374
Hurry, Robert. Finish that egg.

553
00:42:34,083 --> 00:42:38,124
Open the door.

554
00:42:41,291 --> 00:42:43,165
